{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"training-program\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#training-program\" aria-label=\"training program permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Training program</h1>\n<p>This interactive training program is designed to help you understand how to create and edit content using Redocly's developer portal.\nIt's a great companion to our <a href=\"https://docs.redoc.ly/developer-portal/introduction/\">developer portal docs</a>.</p>\n<p>Spend between an hour and a day playing with the most commonly utilized features.</p>\n<h2 id=\"prerequisites\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#prerequisites\" aria-label=\"prerequisites permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Prerequisites</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Basic Git and markdown knowledge</li>\n<li>Node and yarn installed</li>\n<li>A text editor or IDE (we like VS Code)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/developer-portal/setup/\">Setup the developer portal</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"training-exercises\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#training-exercises\" aria-label=\"training exercises permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Training exercises</h2>\n<p>Follow the training exercises sequentially.\nOr cherry-pick them independently if you're limited on time.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/developer-portal/markdown/\">Plain markdown pages</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/developer-portal/awesome/folders/\">Changing the url paths</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/developer-portal/mermaid/\">Markdown with a mermaid diagram</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/developer-portal/page-table-of-contents/\">The page table of contents</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/developer-portal/sidebar-nav/\">Adding a page to the sidebar navigation</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/developer-portal/search/\">Disabling the search box</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/developer-portal/nav-footer/\">Changing nav and footer links</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/developer-portal/logo/\">Change your logo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/developer-portal/metadata/\">Change metadata</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/developer-portal/colors/\">Change your colors</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/developer-portal/typography/\">Change your typography</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/developer-portal/analytics/\">Enable Google Analytics</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/developer-portal/home-page/\">Modify the homepage</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/developer-portal/oas-definitions/\">Modify the OAS definitions</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/developer-portal/mdx/\">Adding a response object to an MDX page</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/developer-portal/upgrade/\">Upgrade to a different version of the developer portal</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Upon completion, you may have questions, or you may be ready to start building your content out.\nLearn how to <a href=\"https://docs.redoc.ly/ci-cd-workflows/\">deploy the developer portal</a> to our global CDN or contact us about purchasing an enterprise license key.</p>\n<h2 id=\"asking-for-help\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#asking-for-help\" aria-label=\"asking for help permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Asking for help</h2>\n<p>Don't be shy... we're here to help.</p>","headings":[{"value":"Training program","depth":1},{"value":"Prerequisites","depth":2},{"value":"Training exercises","depth":2},{"value":"Asking for help","depth":2}]},"contentItem":{"data":{"lastModified":"2021-06-10T07:31:22.000Z","enableToc":null,"disableLastModified":null,"tocMaxDepth":null,"requestLogin":false}},"siteConfig":{"enableToc":true,"disableLastModified":false,"tocMaxDepth":4}},"pageContext":{"matchPath":"","id":"48bf72c1-375b-5fe2-a60a-96ca5ec036de__redocly content/developer-portal/","pageId":"developer-portal/index.md","pageBaseUrl":"/developer-portal/index","title":"Training program","description":"","type":"markdown","data":{"title":"Training program"},"link":"/developer-portal/","sidebarName":"training","isLanding":false,"showPrevButton":null,"showNextButton":null,"apiVersions":null,"apiVersionId":null,"isDefaultApiVersion":null}}